"{\"uid\": \"lbc.co.uk-article-bryony-page-mental-health-olympics-trampoline-5Hjcp7x_2\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Charlotte Lynch  Olympic champion Bryony Page had to tell her brain to \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cshut up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d after struggling with \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cworries and negative thoughts\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d before going on to win gold in the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s trampolining in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"score\": 0.8556135789114669, \"rank\": 0.16875044702387043, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bryony Page\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryony_Page\"}, {\"begin\": 207, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999959073, \"rank\": 4.014602446708602e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to LBC just hours after completing her routine, the world champion said she feared she wouldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t even make it on to the podium.\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999993674464, \"rank\": 6.323395770958701e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cGoing in to it, I felt like maybe I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll finish fifth, maybe I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll miss out on the medals \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 you have all of those worries and all of the negative thoughts going through your brain\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, she said.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy brain is so annoying sometimes, I just have to tell it to shut up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33-year-old, who took silver in Rio 2016 and bronze in Tokyo 2020, said she \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009crefocused\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctried to stay calm in the moment\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, to get her through the show-stopping 10-skill routine which saw her top the leaderboard.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999995199010543, \"rank\": 4.76335316539446e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Britain moves up to third in Olympic medal table, with trampolining, rowing and showjumping golds  Read more:Italian boxer Angela Carini to be awarded prize money by IBA despite Olympic defeat to Algeria's Imane Khelif  Page revealed she made a mistake and downgraded her routine when she was mid-air, so her final trick was not as difficult as she had first intended.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.997328386150648, \"rank\": 0.00267505934396248, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.8605020414431935, \"rank\": 0.09574128505813959, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9996309951463361, \"rank\": 0.0003691307230412651, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999950660843597, \"rank\": 3.338396863749346e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also admitted she had forgotten there was still an athlete left to compete after her, so prematurely celebrated as though she had won gold.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI reacted as if I had already won the gold, and then I remembered there was another person to go.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098at least I know what it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s like to feel like an Olympic champion, even if it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s taken away from me.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t, so we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re all good.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Jess Thom, Team GB\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s lead psychologist told LBC \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not abnormal\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d for athletes to feel anxious.\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1644, \"end\": 1653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Thom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jess Thom\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Thom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Thom\"}, {\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999993674464, \"rank\": 6.323395770958701e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told Matthew Wright: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cOlympians have similar thoughts and feelings to every day people \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 when they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re competing they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re very good at staying in the moment and being present, but it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not abnormal to hear athletes before they get to the start line talking about feeling anxious, and feeling like things could go wrong.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Wright_(basketball)\", \"score\": 0.8023344496027278, \"rank\": 0.18001818783064374, \"text\": \"Matthew Wright\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Wright_(basketball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Wright_(basketball)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThese guys are pros at managing the pressure, they work so hard year on year to prepare for that moment, so they have a really clear idea of what they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re there to do and what success looks like.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They have amazing strategies to manage those unhelpful thoughts and feelings that will inevitably show up\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d, she said.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having achieved the title of World champion and Olympic champion, Page now has her sights set on the circus.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She told LBC: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m hoping that Cirque du Soleil might want me at some point before I get too old.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2524, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999993674464, \"rank\": 6.323395770958701e-10, \"text\": \"LBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cirque du Soleil\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d love to have that experience and perform in front of a crowd in a different way \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve dreamed about that for a really long time so I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d love to have the opportunity to do it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also did not rule out competing in the LA games in 2028 and Brisbane in 2032, and said she hoped Cirque de Soleil would let her return to the circus after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cirque de Soleil\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cirque_du_Soleil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The use of the Ajax vehicle was halted for two weeks to allow an investigation to be carried out  1h ago  The Home Secretary and Foreign Secretary said they had reached \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009can arrangement\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d with the Chinese government on \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cconsolidating\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Beijing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s diplomatic presence in one site  1h ago  The former 'I am A Celebrity' contestant told followers she was suffering from inflammation all over her body  2h ago  The star told fans he had been dealing with a \\\"lot of health issues over the last year\\\"  3h ago  The Supreme Court ruling said the words \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cwoman\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csex\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d in the Equality Act 2010 refer to a biological woman and biological sex  4h ago  Disney fans confused as to why animation needed different titles across the Atlantic  4h ago  With his side losing 17-7 to the New England Patriots on Monday, Koo lined up a 47-yard field goal attempt, as he had done many times before  4h ago  The use of the Ajax vehicle was halted for two weeks to allow an investigation to be carried out  1h ago  The Home Secretary and Foreign Secretary said they had reached \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009can arrangement\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d with the Chinese government on \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cconsolidating\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Beijing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s diplomatic presence in one site  1h ago  The Supreme Court ruling said the words \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cwoman\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csex\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d in the Equality Act 2010 refer to a biological woman and biological sex  4h ago  The officers made \\\"concerted efforts\\\"  to blame fans in the aftermath  5h ago  A 'quality issue' with metal fuselage panels on multiple\\u00c2\\u00a0A320 models has been discovered.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 4493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AFC_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9822936692086515, \"rank\": 0.018025479964334373, \"text\": \"Ajax\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AFC_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AFC_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Secretary\", \"score\": 0.9999999999668034, \"rank\": 3.277826602148715e-11, \"text\": \"Home Secretary\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Secretary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Home_Secretary\"}, {\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"score\": 0.9992686285614977, \"rank\": 0.0006658417428527228, \"text\": \"Chinese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 3639, \"end\": 3645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Walt_Disney_Company\", \"score\": 0.9999661394652585, \"rank\": 3.378027976708261e-05, \"text\": \"Disney\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Walt_Disney_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Walt_Disney_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 3766, \"end\": 3786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_England_Patriots\", \"score\": 0.9886771351504566, \"rank\": 0.011241672151104363, \"text\": \"New England Patriots\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_England_Patriots\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_England_Patriots\"}, {\"begin\": 